records.name: Endheri Sunset Dhangethi

descriptions.direction: Located in Dhangethi, Endheri Sunset is on the Strip and on the beach. The area's natural beauty can be seen at Ari Atoll and Dhangethi Beach. Snorkeling, windsurfing, and fishing offer great chances to get out on the surrounding water, or you can seek out an adventure with ecotours nearby.
descriptions.general: Local Transfer Information To reach the property speedboat ferry, private speed boat hire, public ferryboat or domestic flight can be arranged by the property for which payment will be collected upon check-in. Please contact the property to book your transfer arrangement at least 3 days prior to your arrival. Your arrival and departure flight details and full names of the traveling party will be required. PRIVATE SPEED BOAT HIRE (Duration 90 minutes) Private speed boat service does not have any specific time to travel, and it will be arranged according to the guest`s preferred timings. USD 800 per way (Male to Dhangethi or Dhangethi to Male ). Trip Duration: 80 to 90 minutes. DOMESTIC FLIGHT TRANSFER (Duration: around 15 minutes) Cost: USD 168 per person per way Flights will travel from Male Airport (Velana International Airport) to Maamigili island. (About 5 to 6 flights daily available). And from Maamigili island to Dhangethi Island, a hired speed boat will be charged USD 90 (Around 20 minutes will take for the additional trip). PUBLIC FERRY BOAT (DHONI) (Duration 5 to 6 hrs) Cost: USD 5 per person per way Male city to Dhangethi at 09:00 AM on Saturday, Monday and Wednesday in Villigili Ferry terminal Dhangethi to Male city at 09:00 AM on Sunday, Tuesday and Thursday in Dhangethi Harbor Please note that all of the above transfer options would be provided by a third-party service provider for which the property could not be held responsible. In case of cancellation or delays due to weather or any other condition stated by the third party, the property would cooperate with you in attaining the best available option. Transfer rates are subject to change without prior notice. SCHEDULED SPEED BOAT (Recommended Option) (Duration 90 minutes) Speed boat ferry is available every day (weekly 7 Days) - From Male to Dhangethi or from Dhangethi to Male : USD 35 per person/way - From Airport to Dhangethi or from Dhangethi to Airport: USD 45 per person/way - From Male city to Dhangethi at 04:00 PM from Saturday to Thursday (Departure from Jetty no.1, in Male city) - From Male city to Dhangethi at 03:00 PM on Friday (Departure from Jetty no.1, in Male city) - From Dhangethi to Male city or Airport at 07:00 AM in Dhangethi Harbor A transfer is available during the whole week Guests over 3 years old are considered as adults.
